<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-07-16T14:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-07-16T14:00:00-05:00" n="766" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d766">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 872.48/177</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss> to the Special Agent in Corfu</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_DHP2" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Dodge</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-07-16T15:00:00-04:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">July 16, 1918, 3 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>From Treasury Department:</p>
                        <p>Advised by American Red Cross that Serbian Relief purchases have not been
                            curtailed because of insufficient tonnage and all requirements made by
                            Serbian Minister for foodstuff were promptly taken care of. In very near
                            future further lot of supplies to be shipped weight of which
                            approximates 2,100 tons, and it is expected that ample provision will be
                            made for this space.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName corresp="#p_PFL1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Polk</hi>
                                </persName>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>